&lt;p class=&quot;msg msg--info&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Ordinarily he was insane, but he had lucid moments when&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;he was merely stupid.&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;--HEINRICH HEINE, German critic and poet&lt;/p&gt;
